# CLAUDE.local.md — personal notes (TEMPLATE)

Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` (which is git-ignored) and fill it in. This
is YOUR private layer — personal keys, your own test accounts, scratch notes,
and any working style you want your own agent to follow. It is never committed,
so it won't collide with the other contributor's preferences.

Shared context (architecture, conventions, invariants) goes in `CLAUDE.md`.
Project status / decisions go in `PROJECT_PLAN.md`. Both are committed.

